@niccokunzmann Good point. If so, I propose to leave this as is. Once possible hanging thread is detected, developer should be smart enough to understand if he is interesting in this certain case or not. False reports should not be a big problem once #21 and #31 are implemented. If this will be a problem afterwards then I'd like to get some explanation why this is a problem to help us find the best solution. For now it seems the main problem is the repeating messages.

Btw, I'm still thinking on #31. Probably some examples of real problems are needed to find best solution. Hopefully closing #21 will help us understand where we go next.

